{{italic title}}
The '''''Cascade Alpine Guides''''' are a series of three climbing guides written by [[Fred Beckey]], longtime explorer and climber of the [[Cascade Mountains]] in [[Washington (U.S. state)|Washington]] and [[British Columbia]]. The guides outline routes to summit every peak of any significance in the region.  Many photos in the books were taken by [[United States Geological Survey|USGS]] scientist [[Austin Post]]. The guides are published by [[The Mountaineers (club)|The Mountaineers]].

