'''Güira de Melena Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in the 82nd street in [[Güira de Melena]], [[Cuba]]. It was established as a museum on 11 December 1980.<ref>[http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/408 Museo Municipal de Güira de Melena]</ref>

The museum holds collections on history, weaponry and decorative arts.

