{{Infobox film | name = The Running Actress | image = The Running Actress (film).jpg | alt = | caption = Theatrical poster | film name = {{Film name | hangul = {{linktext|여배우|는| 오늘|도}} | hanja = {{linktext|女俳優}}는 오늘도 | rr = Yeo-bae-u-neun O-neul-do | translation = Today The Actress Is Still…}} | director = [[Moon So-ri]] | producer = Jenna Ku | writer = Moon So-ri | based on = | starring = Moon So-ri | music = | cinematography = Kim Ji-hyun | editing = | studio = | distributor = Metaplay | released = {{film date|2017|09|14}} | runtime = 71 minutes | country = South Korea | language = Korean | budget = | gross = {{USD|124,083}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/films/index/filmsView.jsp?movieCd=20172642|publisher=Korean Film Biz Zone|title=The Running Actress (2017)}}</ref> }}
'''''The Running Actress''''' ({{ko-hhrm|여배우는 오늘도||Yeo-bae-u-neun O-neul-do}}) is a 2017 South Korean [[comedy-drama film]] written, directed by, and starring [[Moon So-ri]].<ref>{{cite web|title=MOON So-ri with her film debut THE RUNNING ACTRESS|url=http://koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/interview.jsp?blbdComCd=601019&seq=281&mode=INTERVIEW_VIEW|website=koreanfilm.or.kr|language=en}}</ref> The feature consists of three separate short films made in the course of Moon’s enrolment at [[Chung-Ang University]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.filmdoo.com/blog/2018/05/08/interview-moon-so-ri-talks-the-running-actress/|title=Interview: Moon So-ri talks The Running Actress|last=|first=|date=2018-05-08|work=FilmDoo|access-date=2018-08-16|language=en-US}}</ref>
==Cast== ===Main=== * [[Moon So-ri]] as Moon So-ri
===Act 1: ''The Actress'' === * Kang Sook as So-ri's friend 1 * Kim Kyung-sun as So-ri's friend 2 * Won Dong-yun as Representative * Kim Rae-won as Representative's junior 1 * Lee Jung-ik as Representative's junior 2 * Yoon Young-kyun as Manager
===Act 2: ''The Running Actress'' === * Seong Byeong-sook as So-ri's mom * Yoon Cho-hee as Yeon-doo * Oh Min-ae as PB team leader * Lee Jeong-eun as Nursing team leader * Seong Jeong-seon as Mother-in-law * Sim Hye-gyoo as Caregiver * [[Lee Jung-hyun]] as Lee Jung-hyun * Lee Seung-hoon as Dental clinic director * Gong Sang-ah as Purser * Kim Sook-in as Producer Oh * Kim In-soo as Film director Kim * [[Jang Joon-hwan]] as So-ri's husband
===Act 3: ''The Best Director'' === * Yoon Sang-hwa as Park Jeong-rak * Jeon Yeo-bin as Lee Seo-yeong * [[Lee Seung-yeon (born 1977)|Lee Seung-yeon]] as Director's wife * Seo Hyo-seung as Director's son * Na Kyung-chan as Director (picture)
